                                        <div class="p-5 border border-b-0 border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700">
                                            <p class="mb-2 text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400">Yes, but inspection of the vehicle is required. However, No Claim Bonus (NCB) can be protected till the expiry of 90 days from the date of expiry.</p>
