                                            <li>Information on claims if any during last year</li>
                                            <li>RC copy</li>
                                        </ul>
                                    </div>
                                    </div>
                                    
                                    
                                    <!-- UNDER WHAT CIRCUMSTANCES INSPECTION OF THE VEHICLE IS REQUIRED? -->
                                    <h2 id="accordion-collapse-heading-4">
                                        <button type="button" class="flex items-center justify-between w-full p-5 font-medium rtl:text-right text-gray-500 border border-gray-200 focus:ring-4 focus:ring-gray-200 dark:focus:ring-gray-800 dark:border-gray-700 dark:text-gray-400 hover:bg-gray-100 dark:hover:bg-gray-800 gap-3" data-accordion-target="#accordion-collapse-body-4" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="accordion-collapse-body-4">
                                            <span>UNDER WHAT CIRCUMSTANCES INSPECTION OF THE VEHICLE IS REQUIRED?</span>
                                            <svg data-accordion-icon class="w-3 h-3 rotate-180 shrink-0" aria-hidden="true" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 10 6">
                                            <path stroke="currentColor" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 5 5 1 1 5"/>
                                            </svg>
                                        </button>
                                    </h2>
                                    <div id="accordion-collapse-body-4" class="hidden" aria-labelledby="accordion-collapse-heading-4">
                                        <div class="p-5 border border-t-0 border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700">
                                            <ul class="ps-5 text-gray-500 list-disc dark:text-gray-400">
                                                <li>If there is a gap in renewal</li>
                                                <li>Switching from third party cover to a comprehensive cover</li>
                                                <li>There is a requirement to cover additional equipment or accessories fitted in car like anti theft device, CNG kit etc. which are not in the expiring policy</li>
                                                <li>Opting for certain specified add on covers</li>
                                            </ul>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>


                                    <!-- WHAT IS THE OWNER’S RESPONSIBILITY IF SOMEONE ELSE IS DRIVING THE VEHICLE AT THE TIME OF ACCIDENT? -->
                                    <h2 id="accordion-collapse-heading-5">
                                        <button type="button" class="flex items-center justify-between w-full p-5 font-medium rtl:text-right text-gray-500 border border-gray-200 focus:ring-4 focus:ring-gray-200 dark:focus:ring-gray-800 dark:border-gray-700 dark:text-gray-400 hover:bg-gray-100 dark:hover:bg-gray-800 gap-3" data-accordion-target="#accordion-collapse-body-5" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="accordion-collapse-body-5">
                                            <span>WHAT IS THE OWNER’S RESPONSIBILITY IF SOMEONE ELSE IS DRIVING THE VEHICLE AT THE TIME OF ACCIDENT?</span>
                                            <svg data-accordion-icon class="w-3 h-3 rotate-180 shrink-0" aria-hidden="true" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 10 6">
                                            <path stroke="currentColor" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 5 5 1 1 5"/>
                                            </svg>
                                        </button>
                                    </h2>
                                    <div id="accordion-collapse-body-5" class="hidden" aria-labelledby="accordion-collapse-heading-5">
                                        <div class="p-5 border border-t-0 border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700">
                                            <p class="mb-2 text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400">Legally anyone driving a car, must hold a valid driving license. In this scenario, it is the owner's responsibility to ensure that his vehicle is being driven by someone with a valid driving license and that the driver is not under the influence of alcohol or drugs.</p>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>


                                    <!-- WHAT IS MULTI-YEAR CAR INSURANCE? -->
                                    <h2 id="accordion-collapse-heading-5">
                                        <button type="button" class="flex items-center justify-between w-full p-5 font-medium rtl:text-right text-gray-500 border border-gray-200 focus:ring-4 focus:ring-gray-200 dark:focus:ring-gray-800 dark:border-gray-700 dark:text-gray-400 hover:bg-gray-100 dark:hover:bg-gray-800 gap-3" data-accordion-target="#accordion-collapse-body-5" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="accordion-collapse-body-5">
                                            <span>WHAT IS MULTI-YEAR CAR INSURANCE?</span>
                                            <svg data-accordion-icon class="w-3 h-3 rotate-180 shrink-0" aria-hidden="true" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 10 6">
                                            <path stroke="currentColor" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 5 5 1 1 5"/>
                                            </svg>
                                        </button>
                                    </h2>
                                    <div id="accordion-collapse-body-5" class="hidden" aria-labelledby="accordion-collapse-heading-5">
                                        <div class="p-5 border border-t-0 border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700">
                                            <p class="mb-2 text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400">According to the Supreme Court order, IRDA has mandated all general insurance companies to offer multi-year third party insurance to all motor vehicles sold after 1st September, 2018. Therefore, instead of single third party liability plans, insurance companies will offer 3 year third party liability plans to cars and 5 year third party liability plans to two wheelers.</p>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>

                            </div>
                            <!-- End of Frequently Asked Questions -->
                            

                        
                        </div>  
                    </div>
                </div>
                <!-- End of Private Cars -->
            </div>





